snippet.title: Chex Quest HD Trailer
snippet.description:
We are excited to share with the Chex Quest community a new trailer for Chex Quest HD! Chex Quest HD is a modern remake of a 1996 advergame which was distributed in millions of boxes of Chex cereal. Like the original, this will be a 5-level, single-player first person shooter suitable for all ages. When completed Chex Quest HD will be free to all who wish to play! Subscribe to the game's Facebook page to get updates on development:

www.facebook.com/ChexQuestHD

CHEX, the Chex Logo and all related materials are the property of General Mills, used with permission.
